data.description: This property can be a permanent residence or a vacation home. A great place to get away from the hustle & bustle of the city life. It is only about 15 minutes from the entrance to Sequoia National Forest.  Plenty of room for all your toys...there are two RV hookup's with power. There are also outdoor showers and outhouse's. In the fall you can pick apple's from the small orchard  or maybe catch a glimpse of the deers eating the apples as well!  This property has a  private pond with bass that is fed by a natural spring.
